    "actor": "https://uofa.net/synth/actor/morrison-credibility-assessor",
    "role": "Credibility assessment team",
    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "The credibility assessment is accepted as a complete package for submission, despite all assessed credibility factors falling below required levels and six factors remaining unassessed. The ContextOfUse does not specify applicability constraints or an operating envelope, meaning the domain of valid model use is implicitly unbounded. This structural omission (W-ON-02) allows the acceptance decision to proceed without formally bounding the conditions under which the CFD hemolysis predictions are considered valid, undermining the traceability of the credibility argument.",
